# Copy to .env and fill in to enable LLM-backed classification and response
# generation. Docker Compose loads .env automatically. Without it, every agent
# runs in pure rules-only mode — the system still works, just without the
# hybrid intelligence layer (see docs/UPGRADE_PLAN.md Phase 2).
#
# Get a free API key at https://openrouter.ai/keys — no payment required for
# ":free"-suffixed models, but they carry tight rate limits (see the plan doc).
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=

# Optional overrides — defaults match these values already, so you only need
# to set these if you want a different model. Check https://openrouter.ai/models
# for current free-tier offerings; they rotate.
# CLASSIFIER_MODEL=meta-llama/llama-3.3-70b-instruct:free
# GENERATION_MODEL=meta-llama/llama-3.3-70b-instruct:free
